            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>cheesy bean burger mixture</strong> and shape into 1 flat patty per person</p><p>Line a tray with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong>, add the <strong>cheesy bean patty[ies]</strong> to the tray and put in the oven for an initial 20 min until starting to crisp</p>",
      "order": 3,
