        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the burger is cooking, deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and slice into thin strips</p><p>Peel and finely slice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
