    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced pepper </strong>and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>sliced onion</strong> (save the rest for later!) cook for 4-5 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, remove from the heat and set aside – this is your <strong>fried onion & pepper</strong></p>",
