      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>smashed avocado</strong> to a <strong>food processor </strong>with the <strong>remaining sliced onion</strong>, juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s] </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Blitz it all up until smooth – this is your <strong>guac</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>remaining ground smoked paprika</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>mayo </strong>and a squeeze of<strong> lime juice </strong>– this is your <strong>smoky paprika mayo</strong></p><p>Slice the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person and set aside until later</p>",
      "order": 6,
