      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the burger is starting to crisp, remove from the oven and top with <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half, then add the <strong>brioche halves </strong>to the opposite side of the tray (cooking for 4 or more? Use two trays!) and return it to the oven for 2-3 min until all the cheese has melted and the brioche is warmed through</p>",
